title: Wood Carving - BMW 420i Convertibles - Woodworking Art

meta.description:
The new BMW 420i Convertibles, BMW 420i is made of wood. The wooden BMW 420i has a removable convertible top that makes this wooden car interesting and unique.
This car was made to order by a my friend and now it belongs to him. If you want to have unique wooden cars in your collection, you can buy at my Etsy online shop: https://www.etsy.com/uk/shop/WoodworkingArtCrafts
